 machines are preferred\nto provide excellent services to our valued customers across the country.\nIf you are searching an expert\nbore well drilling contractor, our company has the greatest\nreputation in this field and bore well drilling expertise in various\ndimensions with depth ranging from 0 to 500 meters.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":532,\"width\":194,\"height\":239} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/asian_group/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/chairman.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-532\" width=\"194\" height=\"239\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><strong>Mr. Ram Sharan Karki </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Chairman</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'WORDS FROM CHAIRMAN', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '544-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-08-15 15:28:51', '2021-08-15 15:28:51', '', '544', 'http://localhost/asian_group/544-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
